Concept information: 

The Moon has been a source of inspiration and observation for thousands of years.

The Moon Goddess has many names and is celebrated in different cultures around the world where they form a central role in mythology.

There is a focus on the alter ego. and a fusion of art, science and technology. In addition, a contemporary anthropology, a study of unusual behaviour of group of humans and animals, either by artistic practices or changes in the habitat.
